0,A man walks into a restaurant and orders an albatross sandwich. He takes one bite and then kills himself.,"The man is blind and he has been lost at sea for weeks, in a lifeboat with two other men, after a shipwreck in which the man’s wife drowned. After some time in the lifeboat, the starving men encounter the body of the blind man’s wife, and they decide to eat it. Knowing the blind man would never agree to eat his wife’s flesh, the other two convince him that they have only found a dead albatross. The blind man is suspicious, and upon being rescued and reaching shore, he walks into a dockside restaurant and orders an albatross sandwich. After one bite of an unfamiliar meat, he realizes what he has been eating."
